#' Demographics
#'
#' Participant demographics collected through an onboarding survey prior to claim assessment. This data 
#' is stored in long format with one row per participant. This data is stored in wide format with one 
#' row per participant. 
#'
#' @format A tibble with 1,027 rows and 91 column variables:
#' \describe{
#' \item{user_name}{Unique, anonymised, alphanumeric identifier for the participant.}
#' \item{Progress}{Percentage of demographics survey completed.}
#' \item{Finished}{Did participant complete demographics survey?}
#' \item{recorded_date}{Date-time survey was completed. In %Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S or yyyy-mm-dd hh:mm:ss format.}
#' \item{ResponseId}{Unique ID for quiz data point.}
#' \item{SCORE_involvement}{Binary indicator for participant involvement in SCORE project outside of human elicited judgements.}
#' \item{english_language_ability}{Participants’ self-rated English language ability.}
