#' \item{field_of_research_Other}{Binary indicator for participant’s field of research being “Other”.}
#' \item{field_of_research_Prefer_Not_To_Say}{Binary indicator for participant not wishing to disclose their field of research.}
#' \item{field_of_research_Other_free_Text}{Participants’ self-reported field of research if no present in list.}
#' \item{current_position_type}{Participants’ current position type selected from list.}
#' \item{current_position_type_free_text}{Participants’ self-reported current position type if not present in list.}
#' \item{career_stage}{Participants’ self-reported career stage selected from list.}
